Package org.neo4j.test.rule

Class EmbeddedDbmsRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.test.rule.ExternalResource
      • org.neo4j.test.rule.DbmsRule
        • org.neo4j.test.rule.EmbeddedDbmsRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.junit.rules.TestRule, GraphDatabaseService, GraphDatabaseAPI
    public class EmbeddedDbmsRule
extends DbmsRule
    JUnit @Rule for configuring, creating and managing an embedded database instance.

    The database instance is created lazily, so configurations can be injected prior to calling DbmsRule.getGraphDatabaseAPI().
